name: Don´t Let them Touch your Qubits!
name_original: Don´t Let them Touch your Qubits!
description:
You are Mr. Qubitto. Keep your qubits safe and untouchable, grab some friends to help you. How many qubits can you keep?

This tiny game was made as part of the GNOJ4 game jam (https://itch.io/jam/games-now-online-jam-4). 

Solo project by Annakaisa Kultima - graphics and code.

Tools used: Construct 3, Adobe Illustrator 24.1.1.

The project has no audio. Sorry.
